# Rock Paper Scissors Game

## Languages used:
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
  
## About The Project:
- A simple javascript rock paper scissors game.
- The computer picks a random move build on a simple if-else statement block.
- The code compares the player and computer moves and decides the result and gives the score accordingly.
- Displays and maintains scores of the game.
- Integrated localStorage to save the scores on the computer system and resets only when reset button is clicked.
- To Display the results on the game screen in-built object DOM is used.

